Draem [
    date: 15-Feb-2008/11:17+3:00
    title: "The Buzzing Club Test"
    slug: %the-buzzing-club-test
    tags: [non-lucid-dream negative]
    old: http://realityhandbook.livejournal.com/65906.html
]

print {I was hooked up to some machine and being shown various pictures in rapid succession on a large multi-color monitor. They were analyzing where in the brain it caused a reaction.}

dialog [

    scientist: {This is interesting, there is a strong reaction tied to the symbol for the card suit of clubs.}

    me: "What?"

    scientist: {Let's see what reactions we get when we subject you to the months of the year...}

]

note {Some of these diagnostic-process situations cause me the most unease, because they make me worry that I'm on some kind of life support somewhere with brain damage and have descended into my own internal reality.}
